## VFS.popd() method

Pops a directory from the directory stack and changes to it.

**Signature:**

```typescript
popd(): Promise<void>;
```
**Returns:**

Promise&lt;void&gt;

Promise that resolves when directory is changed

## Exceptions

VFSError if the directory stack is empty

## Example


```typescript
await fs.popd(); // Return to previously pushed directory
```
